textBox.richText: In my previous two posts, you’ll find that I scored a working 1980 Pac-man cocktail arcade table in amazing condition, and that I was working on restoring every little part of it so that it will easily last another 33 years. Well, I’m proud to say that I’m officially done, and I’ve been playing it like crazy! There really is nothing like playing Pac-man using the original metal joysticks.....;-)
